[section:has_size_type `has_size_type`]

[section Synopsis]
[reference__has_size_type]
[endsect]

[section Description]
This metafunction evaluates to __mpl_true__ if the specified type is defined
with a nested `size_type` type definition that is not `void`.  This
metafunction evaluates to __mpl_false__ otherwise.
[endsect]

[section:definition Where defined]
``
#include <__has_size_type__header__>
``

--or--

``
#include <__ds_traits__header__>
``

Forward declaration:

``
#include <__ds_traits_fwd__header__>
``
[endsect]

[endsect] [/ has_size_type]

